    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "The check that's failing is here: https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/blob/744707a490705f292b0558aa6807b3848a9c4bf9/cmd/utils/flags.go#L1480\r\n\r\nI suspect that the intent is that TxLookupLimit is never _enabled_ on an archive node, in which case maybe a custom check needs can be written that disables txlookupLimit if gcmode archive is set, and possibly warns if default is used and errors if user tries to set any non-zero txlookuplimit with archive mode.",
