    "body": "I see, it was broken in this PR which changed the default value: https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/pull/22293\r\n\r\nSo the easiest fix would be to just make the default `0` again like it was in 1.9.x, I've done that locally and removed the `--txlookuplimit 0` argument and it seems to work fine, in that I can get an old tx ok.\r\n\r\n<details>\r\n\r\n<summary> Old Tx Lookup </summary>\r\n\r\n```\r\n> eth.getBlockByNumber(\"0x11234\", false)\r\n{\r\n  difficulty: \"0x670888c\",\r\n  extraData: \"0xd783010503846765746887676f312e372e33856c696e7578\",\r\n  gasLimit: \"0x47e7c4\",\r\n  gasUsed: \"0x1814b\",\r\n  hash: \"0x6b028480c1448f7de730d45e2418d7fa5c770f8787cae314a0c79bd9ab84df73\",\r\n  logsBloom: \"\",\r\n  miner: \"0x71842f946b98800fe6feb49f0ae4e253259031c9\",\r\n  mixHash: \"0xe7c478ba83aafbaa3fe51a57ce1e438d2f6483539170b486a675330e69e3fa7f\",\r\n  nonce: \"0x03279f51a13b6eb7\",\r\n  number: \"0x11234\",\r\n  parentHash: \"0x077e5aa421a4bd2d4301c81d5e5691c0cf2adfd8af001d8f88ee4059c5f238b4\",\r\n  receiptsRoot: \"0xb8bce07302dd106ed3c3f2dd5ddece21918fcd47e335ba38f037b64e2adac5aa\",\r\n  sha3Uncles: \"0x1dcc4de8dec75d7aab85b567b6ccd41ad312451b948a7413f0a142fd40d49347\",\r\n  size: \"0x2ac\",\r\n  stateRoot: \"0x545d452f5312102278aa6bea6d532acb83286cb6b429da178a35356593dd8589\",\r\n  timestamp: \"0x583f31a3\",\r\n  totalDifficulty: \"0x69bf3d4183f\",\r\n  transactions: [\"0x7554dff405be7b768c8b4065f7990272eb559f0a895bc67e30d54929631591b6\"],\r\n  transactionsRoot: \"0xe814319a70404cb63008ea76f8b5236db22492583d530b7852a19a9d493cbfe9\",\r\n  uncles: []\r\n}\r\n> eth.getTransaction(\"0x7554dff405be7b768c8b4065f7990272eb559f0a895bc67e30d54929631591b6\")\r\n{\r\n  blockHash: \"0x6b028480c1448f7de730d45e2418d7fa5c770f8787cae314a0c79bd9ab84df73\",\r\n  blockNumber: 70196,\r\n  from: \"0x70c9217d814985faef62b124420f8dfbddd96433\",\r\n  gas: 250000,\r\n  gasPrice: 20000000000,\r\n  hash: \"0x7554dff405be7b768c8b4065f7990272eb559f0a895bc67e30d54929631591b6\",\r\n  input: \"0x51a34eb80000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000283164f33da5188000\",\r\n  nonce: 9212,\r\n  r: \"0x9eae614d29ad02f71591e307bebda1002d192c5f33137cafbaa64205bcb155cd\",\r\n  s: \"0x163f4768b99b40a77620cb006af55535ed4f183d54fc189dc1bbcd31acc5d878\",\r\n  to: \"0x8fc6738414035b1e341aa0de00e0657af61e1ca9\",\r\n  transactionIndex: 0,\r\n  type: \"0x0\",\r\n  v: \"0x29\",\r\n  value: 0\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\n</details>",
